profile.longBusinessSummary: Roth Ch Acquisition V Co. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or related business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to identify business opportunities in the field of business services, consumer, healthcare, wellness, technology, and sustainability sectors. Roth Ch Acquisition V Co. was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Newport Beach, California.
